ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: The identifier of this stratifier, as defined in the measure definition.

ivardefs.name: stratum_
ivardefs.desc: This element contains the results for a single stratum within the stratifier. For example, when stratifying on administrative gender, there will be four strata, one for each possible gender value.

properties.desc: When a measure includes multiple stratifiers, there will be a stratifier group for each stratifier defined by the measure.
